      "text": "両手で挟んだ木の棒を、木の板に擦りつけるように\n回転させて摩擦熱で火をおこすのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold a wooden stick between both hands and rotate it against\na wooden board to create fire through friction.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7,
      "endTime": 21.101700782800002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
